OL,4,C'epidemic', Education Secretary says
OL,6,FBridget Phillipson said she will make
OL,7,Fno "apologies" for fining parents with
OL,8,Ffrequently absent children, warning
OL,9,Fthat those who allow their children to
OL,10,Fskip school are significantly denting
OL,11,Ftheir future earning potential.
OL,13,FIn the Sunday Times, Ms Phillipson
OL,14,Fsaid that too many parents allow
OL,15,Fchildren time off for holidays,
OL,16,Fbirthdays or a "runny nose".
OL,18,FHer warning comes as the summer
OL,19,Fholidays come to an end, and pupils
OL,20,Fprepare to return to the classroom
OL,21,Fnext week.
