OL,3,CNumber of children missing school an
OL,4,C'epidemic', Education Secretary says
OL,6,FShe said her first priority is to
OL,7,Fcreate a welcoming environment for
OL,8,Fpupils in a bid to improve attendance.
OL,10,FA report by the Institute for Fiscal
OL,11,FStudies (IFS) published earlier this
OL,12,Fyear said nearly two in five (37%)
OL,13,Fpupils from disadvantaged backgrounds
OL,14,Fare "persistently absent", meaning
OL,15,Fthey miss at least one day of school
OL,16,Fper fortnight on average.
OL,18,FIt noted a spike in absences compared
OL,19,Fwith before the coronavirus pandemic,
OL,20,Fwith students now missing 14 days of
OL,21,Fschool per year on average.
