OL,6,FDuring the general election, Labour
OL,7,Fpromised to cut almost half a million
OL,8,Fdays of school absence as part of its
OL,9,Fplan to deliver free breakfast clubs
OL,10,Fin primary schools in England.
OL,12,FIn June, Ms Phillipson said breakfast
OL,13,Fclubs are proven to "get those
OL,14,Fregularly missing class back into
OL,15,Fschool ` giving them a great start to
OL,16,Ftheir day and getting them ready to
OL,17,Flearn".
